text: The Accounts Management BMF identity theft content previously contained in IRM 21.7.14, Master File (BMF) Identity Theft Procedures for Accounts Management Employees, has been transferred to IRM 25.23.11, Business Master File (BMF) Identity Theft Procedures for Accounts Management, due to operational and administrative change.
This IRM is intended for Wage and Investment, Accounts Management personnel authorized to process Master File (BMF) identity theft inquiries.
